preference.name: RBLDisplayNameWithTypeColumnsShownPref
preference.preference_description: Stores the internal names of RemoteBOMLine properties which display names appear as columns from left-to-right in the BOM Panel in the Product Structure application. This preference value is only a repository, and it is not to be modified other than by the Product Structure code itself.
